  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "CLEANING SERVICES MANAGER",
  "description": "<h2>Job Description</h2><p>We are looking for a <strong>hands-on Cleaning Services Manager</strong> to oversee daily cleaning operations, manage cleaning teams, and ensure high service standards across residential and commercial sites.</p><p>This role suits someone who is operationally strong, people-oriented, and comfortable being on the ground when needed.</p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Oversee daily cleaning operations across multiple sites (residential / commercial)</p></li><li><p>Manage, schedule, and supervise cleaning staff</p></li><li><p>Conduct site inspections and ensure service quality meets company standards</p></li><li><p>Handle client feedback, complaints, and service recovery professionally</p></li><li><p>Train new cleaners on SOPs, safety, and cleaning standards</p></li><li><p>Manage manpower deployment, attendance, and basic performance tracking</p></li><li><p>Coordinate cleaning equipment, supplies, and uniforms</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with NEA, MOM, and workplace safety requirements</p></li><li><p>Prepare simple reports on operations, staffing, and issues</p></li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>2–3 years experience</strong> in cleaning operations or facilities management</p></li><li><p>Experience supervising cleaners or operations teams</p></li><li><p>Familiar with <strong>NEA cleaning standards</strong> and basic safety procedures</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and people-management skills</p></li><li><p>Organised, responsible, and able to handle multiple sites</p></li><li><p>Willing to be hands-on and attend site issues when required</p></li><li><p>Basic computer skills (WhatsApp, scheduling apps, simple reports)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Added advantage:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Experience with commercial cleaning contracts</p></li><li><p>Experience managing foreign workers</p></li></ul><h2>Salary & Benefits</h2><ul><li><p>Salary: <strong>SGD $3,200 – $4,500</strong> (commensurate with experience)</p></li><li><p>Performance bonus / incentives</p></li><li><p>Mobile allowance</p></li><li><p>Career growth opportunity as company expands<br /></p><p>Interested please email detailed resumes with work experience and attached a most recent photo to rachel@jalley.com.sg</p><p>Ow Ting Ting (R2094613)</p><p>Jobs Alley Pte Ltd (21C0599)</p></li></ul>",
